    iex> RockPaperScissorsGuards.play(:rock, :rock)
    "draw!"

    iex> RockPaperScissorsGuards.play(:paper, :paper)
    "draw!"

    iex> RockPaperScissorsGuards.play(:scissors, :scissors)
    "draw!"
  """
